      "speakers": [],
      "text": "端正好",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "滚绣球",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白蜀山水碧蜀山青，圣主朝朝暮暮情。但恨佳人难再得，岂知倾国与倾城！寡人自幸成都，传位太子，改称太上皇。喜得郭子仪兵威大振，指日荡平。只念妃子，为国捐躯，无可表白，特敕成都府建庙一座，又选高手匠人，将旃檀香，雕成妃子生像，命高力士迎进宫来，待寡人亲送入庙供养，敢待来也。咳，想起当时，可怜我那妃子呵！是寡人昧了她誓言深，负了她恩情广。生拆开比翼鸾凤。说甚么生生世世无抛漾，早不道半路里遭魔障！恨寇逼得慌，促驾起的忙，点三千羽林兵将，出延秋便沸沸扬扬。甫伤心第一程，到马嵬驿舍傍，猛地里爆雷般呐起一声的喊响，早则见铁桶似密围住四下里刀枪，恶噷噷单逞着他领军元帅威能大，眼睁睁兵逼拶的俺失势官家气不长，落便手脚慌张。𠲔！可恨那陈元礼呵！（叨叨令）不催他车儿马儿一谜价延延挨挨的望！硬执着言儿语儿一会里喧喧腾腾的谤，更排些戈儿戟儿一哄中重重迭迭的上，生逼个身儿命儿一霎时惊惊惶惶的丧！兀的不痛煞人也么哥！兀的不苦煞人也么哥！闪得俺形儿影儿这一个孤孤凄凄的样！（白）咳！寡人好不悔恨也！",
      "text_length": 438
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "脱布衫羞煞咱俺面悲伤，救不得月貌花庞！是寡人全无主张，不合呵，将他轻放！（小粱州）我当时若肯将身去抵挡，未必她直犯君王。纵然犯了又何妨？泉台上，倒博得永成双！",
      "text_length": 79
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "幺篇",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "我如今独自虽无恙，问余生有甚风光？只落得泪万行，愁千状，人间天上此恨怎能偿？",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高力士上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "数点香泥入庙门，巫山云雨洛川城。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "启万岁爷：杨娘娘宝像已迎到宫门了。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "宣进来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。万岁爷有旨：宣杨娘娘宝像进宫！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫娥"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖大开门〗。太监抬杨贵妃雕像同上，众人进庙。〖大开门收〗。〖朝天子〗。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫娥"
      ],
      "text": "娘娘朝参。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "平身。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "吓，阿呀！妃子吓！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上小楼",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "别离一向，忽看娇样。待与你叙我冤情，说我惊魂，话我愁肠。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "妃子！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上小楼",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "怎不见你回笑庞，答应响，移身前傍？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "吖！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上小楼",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "原来是刻香檀做成的神像！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "高力士！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "传旨马儿在左，车儿在右，朕与娘娘并行者。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。万岁爷有旨：马儿在左，车儿在右，万岁爷亲送娘娘入庙。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫娥",
        "太监"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同幺篇",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "谷碌碌凤车呵，紧贴着行；袅亭亭龙鞭呵，相对着扬。依旧到辇儿厮并，肩儿齐亚，影儿成双。情暗伤心自想，想当时联镳游赏，怎到头来刚做了恁般随唱！",
      "text_length": 69
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖大开门〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "已到庙门，请万岁爷下马。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "宫娥们！伏侍娘娘升座者！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00034",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "宫娥"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。娘娘谢恩。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00035",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "平身。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00036",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00037",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "快活三",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "俺只见有宫娥们簇拥将，把团扇护新妆。犹错认定情初夜入兰房。可怎生冷清清独坐在这影画生绡帐？",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00038",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "看香！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00039",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "朝天子",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "热腾腾宝香，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00040",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "初上香。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00041",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "朝天子",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "映荧荧烛光，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "上香。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "朝天子",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "猛逗着往事来心上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "妃子！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "朝天子",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "记当日在长生殿里御炉旁，对牛女把深盟讲。又谁知信誓荒唐，存殁参商！空忆前盟不暂忘，阿呀妃子吓！今日里我在这厢，你在哪厢。把着这断头香在手掭凄怆！",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "高力士，看酒来，朕与娘娘亲奠一杯。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "是。初赐爵。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "四边静",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "把杯来擎掌，怎能够檀口还从我手内尝？按不住凄惶，叫一声妃子也亲陈上。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "四边静",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "泪珠儿溶溶满觞，溶溶满觞！怕添不下半滴葡萄酿。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00051",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖雁儿落〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00052",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "亚赐爵。终赐爵。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00053",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "四煞",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "奠灵筵礼已终，诉衷情话正长。你娇波不动可见我愁模样？只为我金钗钿盒情辜负，致使你白练黄泉恨渺茫！向此际槌胸想，好一似刀裁了肺腑，火烙了肝肠！",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00054",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "高力士！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00055",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00056",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "你看娘娘脸上流出泪来了。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00057",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "待奴婢看来。咦，果然的流出泪来了！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00058",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "吓！啊呀妃子吓！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00059",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀娘娘吓！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00060",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "三煞",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "只见她垂垂地湿满顾，汪汪地含在眶，纷纷地点滴在神台上。分明是牵衣请死愁容貌，回顾吞声惨面庞。这伤心真无两。休说是泥人堕泪，便教那铁汉也肠慌！",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00061",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士"
      ],
      "text": "万岁爷请免悲伤，待奴婢们叩见娘娘。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00062",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高力士、众人同拜。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00063",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "高力士",
        "宫娥"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀娘娘吓！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00064",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00065",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二煞",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "只见老常侍双膝跪，旧宫娥伙地伤，叫不出娘娘千岁，一个个含悲向。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00066",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "妃子！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902132_e00067",
      "play_id": "70902132",
      "scene_id": "70902132_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "二煞",
      "speakers": [
        "唐明皇"
      ],
      "text": "只为你当日在昭阳殿里施恩遍，今日个锦水祠中遗爱长。悲风荡，肠断煞数声杜宇，半壁斜阳！",
      "text_length": 42
